title: YES GIRL YES!
body:
This is the best day if my life. You don't understand.

https://i.gyazo.com/a605bb6e46495498510cc2770af5b05e.png

My speed has like, octapussed!. Downloading at 250kb/s no more! 

https://i.gyazo.com/bcc4f7384dc04bf462e7a8bfa0f7153b.png

Okay, well, that's bad. But look at that peak speed! Oh, my God, my manparts are at full attention right now.

replies.body: I went from 350kbps to 30mbps with nbn FeelsGoodMan
Mine is faster, same as Rougestoney... but only 8 ping i win

i remember the days when 56 kbit/s was the shit and you had to dial up to the interwebs and actually watch and wait for pages load like a peasant.
Jesus my peak has always been 3 MB/s who are you with?
